- `edgeSet (cons h p) = insert (Sym2.mk (u, v')) (edgeSet p)`
- `card (supportSet (cons h p)) = card (insert u (supportSet p))`
- `card (edgeSet (cons h p)) = card (insert (Sym2.mk (u, v')) (edgeSet p))`
- By induction hypothesis: `card (supportSet p) ≤ card (edgeSet p) + 1`
- We need to show: `card (insert u (supportSet p)) ≤ card (insert (Sym2.mk (u, v')) (edgeSet p)) + 1`

