- `[p.start]` for `p = nil` (where `p.start` is `u`)
- `p.start :: p.tail.support` for `p = cons h q` (where `p.tail` is `q`)
- `p.start :: p.tail.support` for `p = loop q` (where `p.tail` is `q`)

