The edge set of `cons h p` is `h :: p.edgeSet` (where `h` is the edge `Sym2.mk (u, v')`). So, its cardinality is `(p.edgeSet).card + 1`.

So the inequality becomes: `(p.supportSet).card + 1 ≤ (p.edgeSet).card + 1 + 1`.

This simplifies to `(p.supportSet).card ≤ (p.edgeSet).card + 1`, which is exactly the induction hypothesis.

