The edge set of `cons h p` is `insert h (p.edgeSet)`. The cardinality is `1 + (p.edgeSet).card`.

So the inequality becomes: `1 + (p.supportSet).card ≤ 1 + (p.edgeSet).card + 1`.

This simplifies to `(p.supportSet).card ≤ (p.edgeSet).card + 1`, which is the induction hypothesis.

So the induction step is correct. The Lean proof would be:

